間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34d8a2b517a990ffc4d0bbe09f5d7b4088f02c2","tid":240224,"uid":12712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T00:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔專既話讀完咪又係晒錢晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢應該係想讀個degree易啲升職啫"},{"pid":"8daffdb8522c0d1129db575a62fad9ed39562ad4","tid":240224,"uid":87215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔專既話讀完咪又係晒錢晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢應該係想讀個degree易啲升職啫</blockquote><br />\n都唔係升唔升職咁複雜，純粹係有個degree 多張入場卷，個學歷點都叫大學生咁姐"},{"pid":"f2f00b6dd0e4b07cd169af52cc7a611d0d4fbfc7","tid":240224,"uid":87215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔專既話讀完咪又係晒錢晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係純粹想個學歷唔咁難睇，都可以稱得上大學生咁。頹科真係唔緊要，就係唔聽晒咁多時間所以想揀個短年期既讀"},{"pid":"f0fe3ad95c4c178e14651054fa49b157d51ed683","tid":240224,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:41:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}